    "## Get Deflock location by using OpenStreetMap \n",
    "- Deflock: https://deflock.org/map (Used to help ground truth the LPR.)\n",
    "- OpoenStreetMap overpass turbo: https://overpass-turbo.eu/# (Used to get the LPR location.)"
   ]
  },
